#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn35.131"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.131:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.131:0.2"
msgid "13. Gahapativagga "
msgstr "13. Householders "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 131. Nakulapitusutta → nakulapitā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.131:0.3"
msgid "131. Nakulapitusutta "
msgstr "131. Nakula’s Father "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn35.131:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā bhaggesu viharati susumāragire bhesakaḷāvane migadāye. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Bhaggas on Crocodile Hill, in the deer park at Bhesakaḷā’s Wood. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.131:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho nakulapitā gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho nakulapitā gahapati bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the householder Nakula’s father went up to the Buddha … and asked him, "

msgctxt "sn35.131:1.3"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme no parinibbāyanti? "
msgstr "“What is the cause, sir, what is the reason why some sentient beings aren’t fully extinguished in the present life? "

msgctxt "sn35.131:1.4"
msgid "Ko pana, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme parinibbāyantī”ti? "
msgstr "What is the cause, sir, what is the reason why some sentient beings are fully extinguished in the present life?” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.131:1.5"
msgid "“Santi kho, gahapati, cakkhuviññeyyā rūpā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā piyarūpā kāmūpasaṃhitā rajanīyā. "
msgstr "(This should be told in full as in SN 35.118.) "

msgctxt "sn35.131:1.6"
msgid "Tañce bhikkhu abhinandati abhivadati ajjhosāya tiṭṭhati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:1.7"
msgid "Tassa taṃ abhinandato abhivadato ajjhosāya tiṭṭhato tannissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ hoti tadupādānaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:1.8"
msgid "Saupādāno, gahapati, bhikkhu no parinibbāyati … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:1.9"
msgid "santi kho, gahapati, jivhāviññeyyā rasā … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:1.10"
msgid "santi kho, gahapati, manoviññeyyā dhammā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā piyarūpā kāmūpasaṃhitā rajanīyā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:1.11"
msgid "Tañce bhikkhu abhinandati abhivadati ajjhosāya tiṭṭhati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:1.12"
msgid "Tassa taṃ abhinandato abhivadato ajjhosāya tiṭṭhato tannissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ hoti tadupādānaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:1.13"
msgid "Saupādāno, gahapati, bhikkhu no parinibbāyati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:1.14"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, gahapati, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme no parinibbāyanti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn35.131:2.1"
msgid "Santi ca kho, gahapati, cakkhuviññeyyā rūpā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā piyarūpā kāmūpasaṃhitā rajanīyā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:2.2"
msgid "Tañce bhikkhu nābhinandati nābhivadati nājjhosāya tiṭṭhati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:2.3"
msgid "Tassa taṃ anabhinandato anabhivadato anajjhosāya tiṭṭhato na tannissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ hoti, na tadupādānaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:2.4"
msgid "Anupādāno, gahapati, bhikkhu parinibbāyati … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:2.5"
msgid "santi kho, gahapati, jivhāviññeyyā rasā … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:2.6"
msgid "santi kho, gahapati, manoviññeyyā dhammā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā piyarūpā kāmūpasaṃhitā rajanīyā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:2.7"
msgid "Tañce bhikkhu nābhinandati nābhivadati nājjhosāya tiṭṭhati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:2.8"
msgid "Tassa taṃ nābhinandato nābhivadato anajjhosāya tiṭṭhato na tannissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ hoti na tadupādānaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:2.9"
msgid "Anupādāno, gahapati, bhikkhu parinibbāyati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.131:2.10"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, gahapati, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme parinibbāyantī”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.131:2.11"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
